data.description: The perfect mountain home with park-like setting is waiting for you. This home offers main level living with three bedrooms and two full baths. Great covered porch for your morning coffee and sounds of the creek. The yard around the house is flat and there is plenty of parking for your RV and Boat. Fenced in dog area and chicken coop included. A "man-cave" out-building has electric. The lake is just a few minutes away for boating and fishing.  Just reduced and paying $1500 in closing cost!!!!!!!
